SEVERAL cops found themselves in a predicament when they had to deal with the naked truth. A video of a naked man being chased by cops has surfaced on social media. In the video, cops can be seen following the man in several police cars. The police cars manage to stop and corner the naked man. However, the man manages to escape from the cops â€“ in the process of escaping one of the cops falls. The fact that the cop fell while trying to arrest the man had social media in stitches and asking if the cop is even competent. Eastern Cape cops said the man is mentally disturbed and he was spotted by patrolling cops on the N2 highway outside Port Elizabeth. According to cops he was arrested and handed over to a mental hospital. 